			<h2>Tavern Books is supported by the generosity of individuals, family foundations, and corporations. When you support the press with a tax-deductible donation, you enable us to continue working with the world’s finest poets and translators, and to advocate for the literary arts on an international scale.</h2> 
			<p class="lead">Your gift can be made using our secure online “Donate” button, or by sending a check written to “Tavern Books” with the word “Donation” in the memo line.<br><br>
